                            <comment id="17304731" author="bereng" created="Fri, 19 Mar 2021 08:52:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The problem was that the assert relied on a number which was an &lt;a href=&quot;https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/util/concurrent/ThreadPoolExecutor.html#getActiveCount--&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;approximation&lt;/a&gt; of the value we needed. The fix is to either remove that assert or to poll the value. I chose the later for no particular reason and it passes locally now 10K runs whereas it would fail before.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
